# Paths the remote backend (Terrakube) must not package when uploading the
# config for a remote plan/apply. tofu honors this file when bundling.
#
# Without it, the Nix dev shell's .direnv/ (which contains symlinks into the
# Nix store) breaks the upload the moment the store path is garbage-collected:
#   Error: Failed to upload configuration files: ... lstat .../.direnv/...: no
#   such file or directory
# .git/ and .terraform/ are excluded by tofu's defaults; .direnv/ is not.
.direnv/
.terraform/
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
crash.log
